       IDENTIFICATION DIVISION.
       PROGRAM-ID.    COI78104.
      ******************************************************************
      *     PROGRAMA COI78104.                                         *
      *                                                                *
      *     Invoices                                                   *
      ******************************************************************
      *     LOG ALTERACOES:                                            *
      *   USER     / DATA     /   REFERENCIA / OBSERVACOES             *
      *                                                                *
      *                                                                *
      ******************************************************************
       ENVIRONMENT DIVISION.
       CONFIGURATION SECTION.
       DATA DIVISION.
      *--------------------------------------------------------------
       WORKING-STORAGE SECTION.
      *--------------------------------------------------------------
       01  FILLER                          PIC X(40) VALUE
           'INICIO WORKING-STORAGE COI78104         '.
      *--------------------------------------------------------------
      *            DECLARACOES DE DB2
      *--------------------------------------------------------------
           EXEC SQL INCLUDE COCD3605 END-EXEC.
           EXEC SQL INCLUDE COCD5012 END-EXEC.
           EXEC SQL INCLUDE SQLCA    END-EXEC.
      *--------------------------------------------------------------
       01 WS-SQL-AUXILIARY.
         05 IND-NULL                       PIC S9(04) BINARY.

      *--------------------------------------------------------------
      *            VARIAVEIS
      *--------------------------------------------------------------
       01  WS-VARIAVEIS.
           05 WS-NRETAMOUNT1               PIC S9(15)V9(02) COMP-3.
           05 WS-NRETTAX1                  PIC S9(15)V9(02) COMP-3.
           05 WS-NRETAMOUNT2               PIC S9(15)V9(02) COMP-3.
           05 WS-NRETTAX2                  PIC S9(15)V9(02) COMP-3.
           05 WS-NRETAMOUNT3               PIC S9(15)V9(02) COMP-3.
           05 WS-NRETTAX3                  PIC S9(15)V9(02) COMP-3.
           05 WS-NRETAMOUNT4               PIC S9(15)V9(02) COMP-3.
           05 WS-NRETTAX4                  PIC S9(15)V9(02) COMP-3.
      *--------------------------------------------------------------
      *            MENSAGEM DE INPUT E  OUTPUT
      *--------------------------------------------------------------
       COPY COCV7810.
       COPY COCV7811.

      *--------------------------------------------------------------
      *            AREAS DE TRABALHO
      *--------------------------------------------------------------
       COPY VIAL0010.
       COPY VIAL0015.
       COPY VIAW0005.
       COPY VIAK0001.
       COPY VIAK0002.
       COPY COCK0001.
       COPY COCK0002.

       COPY ETCK0001.
       COPY ETCK0002.
       COPY COCL5005.
       COPY ETCL0002.
       COPY AQCW0005.

      *--------------------------------------------------------------
      *            CONSTANTES
      *--------------------------------------------------------------
       01  WS-CONSTANTES.
           05 CON-COVT3605 PIC X(08) VALUE 'COVT3605'.
           05 CON-COVT5012 PIC X(08) VALUE 'COVT5012'.
           05 CON-0        PIC X(01) VALUE '0'.

      *--------------------------------------------------------------
      * PROGRAM CONTROL
      *--------------------------------------------------------------
       01  WS-PROGRAM-CONTROL.
           05 WS-PROGNAME     PIC  X(08) VALUE 'COI78104'.
      *--------------------------------------------------------------
       01  FILLER                        PIC X(40) VALUE
           'FIM DA WORKING-STORAGE COI78104         '.
      *--------------------------------------------------------------
       LINKAGE SECTION.
      *--------------------------------------------------------------
       COPY VIAL0004.

            EXEC SQL INCLUDE VIAP0009 END-EXEC.

      *--------------------------------------------------------------
      *            0000-MAINLINE
      *--------------------------------------------------------------
       0000-MAINLINE.

           PERFORM 1000-INICIO-PROGRAMA
              THRU 1099-INICIO-PROGRAMA-EXIT.

           PERFORM 2000-PROC-PROGRAMA
              THRU 2099-PROC-PROGRAMA-EXIT.

           PERFORM 3000-FINAL-PROGRAMA
              THRU 3099-FINAL-PROGRAMA-EXIT.

       0099-MAINLINE-EXIT.
           COPY VIAP0004.
      *--------------------------------------------------------------
      *            1000-INICIO-PROGRAMA
      *--------------------------------------------------------------
       1000-INICIO-PROGRAMA.

           IF VIAL0001-DEBUG-SIM
              MOVE '1000-INICIO-PROGRAMA'  TO VIAL0015-CALLER-ID
              MOVE 'VIAL0001-MENSAGEM-INPUT' TO VIAL0015-CAMPO-NM(1)
              MOVE  VIAL0001-MENSAGEM-INPUT  TO VIAL0015-CAMPO-VLR(1)
              PERFORM VIAP0016-TRATA-DEBUG
                 THRU VIAP0016-TRATA-DEBUG-EXIT
           END-IF.

           MOVE VIAL0001-MENSAGEM-INPUT    TO COCV7810-MSG.
           MOVE COCV7810-ASE               TO COCV7811-ASE.

       1099-INICIO-PROGRAMA-EXIT.
           EXIT.
      *--------------------------------------------------------------
      *            2000-PROC-PROGRAMA
      *--------------------------------------------------------------
       2000-PROC-PROGRAMA.

           IF VIAL0001-DEBUG-SIM
              MOVE '2000-PROC-PROGRAMA'    TO VIAL0015-CALLER-ID
              PERFORM VIAP0016-TRATA-DEBUG
                 THRU VIAP0016-TRATA-DEBUG-EXIT
           END-IF.

           MOVE COCV7810-ADE               TO COCV7811-ADE.

           IF VIAL0002-SEM-ERROS
              PERFORM 2100-VALIDACOES
                 THRU 2199-VALIDACOES-EXIT
           END-IF.

           IF VIAL0002-SEM-ERROS
              PERFORM 2200-INSERE-DADOS
                 THRU 2299-INSERE-DADOS-EXIT
           END-IF.

       2099-PROC-PROGRAMA-EXIT.
           EXIT.
      *--------------------------------------------------------------
      *                   2100-VALIDACOES
      *--------------------------------------------------------------
       2100-VALIDACOES.

           IF VIAL0001-DEBUG-SIM
              MOVE '2100-VALIDACOES'       TO VIAL0015-CALLER-ID
              PERFORM VIAP0016-TRATA-DEBUG
                 THRU VIAP0016-TRATA-DEBUG-EXIT
           END-IF.

      *--- VALIDA SE TODAS AS QUATRO OCORRENCIAS ESTAO VAZIAS
           IF VIAL0002-SEM-ERROS
              IF  ( COCV7810-DDATAEMISS1   EQUAL SPACES
              OR    COCV7810-DDATAEMISS1   EQUAL COCK0002-DATA-MIN )
              AND ( COCV7810-DDATEDUE1     EQUAL SPACES
              OR    COCV7810-DDATEDUE1     EQUAL COCK0002-DATA-MIN )
              AND ( COCV7810-CPRAZO1       EQUAL SPACES )
              AND ( COCV7810-CTIPFAC1      EQUAL SPACES )
              AND ( COCV7810-NTOTALAMOUNT1 EQUAL ZEROS )
              AND ( COCV7810-CIMPOSTO1     EQUAL SPACES )
              AND ( COCV7810-NTAXAMOUNT1   EQUAL ZEROS )
              AND ( COCV7810-GDESCINVOICE1 EQUAL SPACES )
              AND ( COCV7810-NOTAS1        EQUAL SPACES )
              AND
                  ( COCV7810-DDATAEMISS2   EQUAL SPACES
              OR    COCV7810-DDATAEMISS2   EQUAL COCK0002-DATA-MIN )
              AND ( COCV7810-DDATEDUE2     EQUAL SPACES
              OR    COCV7810-DDATEDUE2     EQUAL COCK0002-DATA-MIN )
              AND ( COCV7810-CPRAZO2       EQUAL SPACES )
              AND ( COCV7810-CTIPFAC2      EQUAL SPACES )
              AND ( COCV7810-NTOTALAMOUNT2 EQUAL ZEROS )
              AND ( COCV7810-CIMPOSTO2     EQUAL SPACES )
              AND ( COCV7810-NTAXAMOUNT2   EQUAL ZEROS )
              AND ( COCV7810-GDESCINVOICE2 EQUAL SPACES )
              AND ( COCV7810-NOTAS2        EQUAL SPACES )
              AND
                  ( COCV7810-DDATAEMISS3   EQUAL SPACES
              OR    COCV7810-DDATAEMISS3   EQUAL COCK0002-DATA-MIN )
              AND ( COCV7810-DDATEDUE3     EQUAL SPACES
              OR    COCV7810-DDATEDUE3     EQUAL COCK0002-DATA-MIN )
              AND ( COCV7810-CPRAZO3       EQUAL SPACES )
              AND ( COCV7810-CTIPFAC3      EQUAL SPACES )
              AND ( COCV7810-NTOTALAMOUNT3 EQUAL ZEROS )
              AND ( COCV7810-CIMPOSTO3     EQUAL SPACES )
              AND ( COCV7810-NTAXAMOUNT3   EQUAL ZEROS )
              AND ( COCV7810-GDESCINVOICE3 EQUAL SPACES )
              AND ( COCV7810-NOTAS3        EQUAL SPACES )
              AND
                  ( COCV7810-DDATAEMISS4   EQUAL SPACES
              OR    COCV7810-DDATAEMISS4   EQUAL COCK0002-DATA-MIN )
              AND ( COCV7810-DDATEDUE4     EQUAL SPACES
              OR    COCV7810-DDATEDUE4     EQUAL COCK0002-DATA-MIN )
              AND ( COCV7810-CPRAZO4       EQUAL SPACES )
              AND ( COCV7810-CTIPFAC4      EQUAL SPACES )
              AND ( COCV7810-NTOTALAMOUNT4 EQUAL ZEROS )
              AND ( COCV7810-CIMPOSTO4     EQUAL SPACES )
              AND ( COCV7810-NTAXAMOUNT4   EQUAL ZEROS )
              AND ( COCV7810-GDESCINVOICE4 EQUAL SPACES )
              AND ( COCV7810-NOTAS4        EQUAL SPACES )
                MOVE VIAK0002-ERROS-FUNCAO  TO VIAL0002-IND-ERROS
                MOVE COCK0002-STATUS-ACTIVO TO COCV7811-DUMMYFIELD-S
                MOVE COCK0001-OC-VAZIAS     TO COCV7811-DUMMYFIELD-MSG
                MOVE COCK0002-CAPLIC     TO COCV7811-DUMMYFIELD-CAPLIC
           END-IF.

           IF VIAL0002-SEM-ERROS
              PERFORM 2300-OBTEM-CEMPRESA
                 THRU 2399-OBTEM-CEMPRESA-EXIT
           END-IF.


      *--- VALIDAR A PRIMEIRA OCORRENCIA
      *--- Só valida se a ocorrencia tiver campos valorizados
           IF VIAL0002-SEM-ERROS
              IF  ( COCV7810-DDATAEMISS1   EQUAL SPACES
              OR    COCV7810-DDATAEMISS1   EQUAL COCK0002-DATA-MIN )
              AND ( COCV7810-DDATEDUE1     EQUAL SPACES
              OR    COCV7810-DDATEDUE1     EQUAL COCK0002-DATA-MIN )
              AND ( COCV7810-CPRAZO1       EQUAL SPACES )
              AND ( COCV7810-CTIPFAC1      EQUAL SPACES )
              AND ( COCV7810-NTOTALAMOUNT1 EQUAL ZEROS )
              AND ( COCV7810-CIMPOSTO1     EQUAL SPACES )
              AND ( COCV7810-NTAXAMOUNT1   EQUAL ZEROS )
              AND ( COCV7810-GDESCINVOICE1 EQUAL SPACES )
              AND ( COCV7810-NOTAS1        EQUAL SPACES )
                    CONTINUE
              ELSE
                PERFORM 2500-VALIDA-OC1
                   THRU 2500-VALIDA-OC1-EXIT
              END-IF
           END-IF.

      *--- VALIDAR A SEGUNDA OCORRENCIA
      *--- Só valida se a ocorrencia tiver campos valorizados
           IF VIAL0002-SEM-ERROS
              IF  ( COCV7810-DDATAEMISS2   EQUAL SPACES
              OR    COCV7810-DDATAEMISS2   EQUAL COCK0002-DATA-MIN )
              AND ( COCV7810-DDATEDUE2     EQUAL SPACES
              OR    COCV7810-DDATEDUE2     EQUAL COCK0002-DATA-MIN )
              AND ( COCV7810-CPRAZO2       EQUAL SPACES )
              AND ( COCV7810-CTIPFAC2      EQUAL SPACES )
              AND ( COCV7810-NTOTALAMOUNT2 EQUAL ZEROS )
              AND ( COCV7810-CIMPOSTO2     EQUAL SPACES )
              AND ( COCV7810-NTAXAMOUNT2   EQUAL ZEROS )
              AND ( COCV7810-GDESCINVOICE2 EQUAL SPACES )
              AND ( COCV7810-NOTAS2        EQUAL SPACES )
                    CONTINUE
              ELSE
                PERFORM 2500-VALIDA-OC2
                   THRU 2500-VALIDA-OC2-EXIT
              END-IF
           END-IF.

      *--- VALIDAR A TERCEIRA OCORRENCIA
      *--- Só valida se a ocorrencia tiver campos valorizados
           IF VIAL0002-SEM-ERROS
              IF  ( COCV7810-DDATAEMISS3   EQUAL SPACES
              OR    COCV7810-DDATAEMISS3   EQUAL COCK0002-DATA-MIN )
              AND ( COCV7810-DDATEDUE3     EQUAL SPACES
              OR    COCV7810-DDATEDUE3     EQUAL COCK0002-DATA-MIN )
              AND ( COCV7810-CPRAZO3       EQUAL SPACES )
              AND ( COCV7810-CTIPFAC3      EQUAL SPACES )
              AND ( COCV7810-NTOTALAMOUNT3 EQUAL ZEROS )
              AND ( COCV7810-CIMPOSTO3     EQUAL SPACES )
              AND ( COCV7810-NTAXAMOUNT3   EQUAL ZEROS )
              AND ( COCV7810-GDESCINVOICE3 EQUAL SPACES )
              AND ( COCV7810-NOTAS3        EQUAL SPACES )
                    CONTINUE
              ELSE
                PERFORM 2500-VALIDA-OC3
                   THRU 2500-VALIDA-OC3-EXIT
              END-IF
           END-IF.

      *--- VALIDAR A QUARTA OCORRENCIA
      *--- Só valida se a ocorrencia tiver campos valorizados
           IF VIAL0002-SEM-ERROS
              IF  ( COCV7810-DDATAEMISS4   EQUAL SPACES
              OR    COCV7810-DDATAEMISS4   EQUAL COCK0002-DATA-MIN )
              AND ( COCV7810-DDATEDUE4     EQUAL SPACES
              OR    COCV7810-DDATEDUE4     EQUAL COCK0002-DATA-MIN )
              AND ( COCV7810-CPRAZO4       EQUAL SPACES )
              AND ( COCV7810-CTIPFAC4      EQUAL SPACES )
              AND ( COCV7810-NTOTALAMOUNT4 EQUAL ZEROS )
              AND ( COCV7810-CIMPOSTO4     EQUAL SPACES )
              AND ( COCV7810-NTAXAMOUNT4   EQUAL ZEROS )
              AND ( COCV7810-GDESCINVOICE4 EQUAL SPACES )
              AND ( COCV7810-NOTAS4        EQUAL SPACES )
                    CONTINUE
              ELSE
                PERFORM 2500-VALIDA-OC4
                   THRU 2500-VALIDA-OC4-EXIT
              END-IF
           END-IF.

       2199-VALIDACOES-EXIT.
           EXIT.

      *--------------------------------------------------------------
      *                 2300-OBTEM-CEMPRESA
      *--------------------------------------------------------------
        2300-OBTEM-CEMPRESA.

            IF VIAL0001-DEBUG-SIM
               MOVE '2300-OBTEM-CEMPRESA' TO VIAL0015-CALLER-ID
               PERFORM VIAP0016-TRATA-DEBUG
                  THRU VIAP0016-TRATA-DEBUG-EXIT
            END-IF.

            MOVE COCV7810-NIDPROJECTO  TO COCD3605-NIDPROJECTO.
            MOVE COCV7810-GCLIENTE     TO COCD3605-CLIENTE.

            EXEC SQL
                  SELECT  CEMPRESA, PAIS
                    INTO :COCD3605-CEMPRESA, :COCD3605-PAIS
                  FROM    COVT3605_PROJECTS
                  WHERE   NIDPROJECTO = :COCD3605-NIDPROJECTO
                    AND   CLIENTE     = :COCD3605-CLIENTE
            END-EXEC.

            MOVE CON-COVT3605 TO VIAL0002-TABLE-NAME.
            PERFORM 9020-DB2CHECK
               THRU 9029-DB2CHECK-EXIT.

            IF VIAL0002-SEM-ERROS
               IF NOT DB2-OK
                  MOVE VIAK0002-ERROS-FUNCAO
                    TO VIAL0002-IND-ERROS
                  MOVE COCK0002-STATUS-ACTIVO
                    TO COCV7811-NIDPROJECTO-S
                  MOVE COCK0001-NIDPROJECTO-N-EXISTS
                    TO COCV7811-NIDPROJECTO-MSG
                  MOVE COCK0002-CAPLIC
                    TO COCV7811-NIDPROJECTO-CAPLIC
               END-IF
            END-IF.


       2399-OBTEM-CEMPRESA-EXIT.
           EXIT.

      *--------------------------------------------------------------
      *--- 2500-VALIDACOES PRIMEIRA OCORRENCIA
      *--------------------------------------------------------------
       2500-VALIDA-OC1.

           IF VIAL0001-DEBUG-SIM
              MOVE '2500-VALIDA-OC1' TO VIAL0015-CALLER-ID
              PERFORM VIAP0016-TRATA-DEBUG
                 THRU VIAP0016-TRATA-DEBUG-EXIT
           END-IF.

      *--- Data de Prevista de Emissao
           IF VIAL0002-SEM-ERROS
             IF COCV7810-DDATAEMISS1 EQUAL SPACES
             OR COCV7810-DDATAEMISS1 EQUAL COCK0002-DATA-MIN
                MOVE VIAK0002-ERROS-FUNCAO  TO VIAL0002-IND-ERROS
                MOVE COCK0002-STATUS-ACTIVO TO COCV7811-DDATAEMISS1-S
                MOVE COCK0001-CAMPO-OBRIGAT TO COCV7811-DDATAEMISS1-MSG
                MOVE COCK0002-CAPLIC     TO COCV7811-DDATAEMISS1-CAPLIC
             END-IF
           END-IF.

      *--- Data de Vencimento
           IF VIAL0002-SEM-ERROS
             IF COCV7810-DDATEDUE1   EQUAL SPACES
             OR COCV7810-DDATEDUE1   EQUAL COCK0002-DATA-MIN
                MOVE VIAK0002-ERROS-FUNCAO  TO VIAL0002-IND-ERROS
                MOVE COCK0002-STATUS-ACTIVO TO COCV7811-DDATEDUE1-S
                MOVE COCK0001-CAMPO-OBRIGAT TO COCV7811-DDATEDUE1-MSG
                MOVE COCK0002-CAPLIC     TO COCV7811-DDATEDUE1-CAPLIC
             END-IF
           END-IF.

      *--- Data de Vencimento versus Data Prevista de Emissao
           IF VIAL0002-SEM-ERROS
             IF  COCV7810-DDATEDUE1 NOT EQUAL SPACES
             AND COCV7810-DDATEDUE1 NOT EQUAL COCK0002-DATA-MIN
             AND COCV7810-DDATEDUE1 < COCV7810-DDATAEMISS1
                MOVE VIAK0002-ERROS-FUNCAO  TO VIAL0002-IND-ERROS
                MOVE COCK0002-STATUS-ACTIVO TO COCV7811-DDATEDUE1-S
                MOVE COCK0001-DTVEN-INV     TO COCV7811-DDATEDUE1-MSG
                MOVE COCK0002-CAPLIC     TO COCV7811-DDATEDUE1-CAPLIC
             END-IF
           END-IF.

      *--- Prazo Vencimento
           IF VIAL0002-SEM-ERROS
             IF COCV7810-CPRAZO1     EQUAL SPACES
                MOVE VIAK0002-ERROS-FUNCAO  TO VIAL0002-IND-ERROS
                MOVE COCK0002-STATUS-ACTIVO TO COCV7811-CPRAZO1-S
                MOVE COCK0001-CAMPO-OBRIGAT TO COCV7811-CPRAZO1-MSG
                MOVE COCK0002-CAPLIC     TO COCV7811-CPRAZO1-CAPLIC
             END-IF
           END-IF.

      *--- Tipo de Factura
           IF VIAL0002-SEM-ERROS
             IF COCV7810-CTIPFAC1 EQUAL SPACES
                MOVE VIAK0002-ERROS-FUNCAO  TO VIAL0002-IND-ERROS
                MOVE COCK0002-STATUS-ACTIVO TO COCV7811-CTIPFAC1-S
                MOVE COCK0001-CAMPO-OBRIGAT TO COCV7811-CTIPFAC1-MSG
                MOVE COCK0002-CAPLIC     TO COCV7811-CTIPFAC1-CAPLIC
             END-IF
           END-IF.

      *--- Valor Liquido
           IF VIAL0002-SEM-ERROS
             IF COCV7810-NTOTALAMOUNT1 EQUAL ZEROS
                MOVE VIAK0002-ERROS-FUNCAO  TO VIAL0002-IND-ERROS
                MOVE COCK0002-STATUS-ACTIVO
                                     TO COCV7811-NTOTALAMOUNT1-S
                MOVE COCK0001-CAMPO-OBRIGAT
                                     TO COCV7811-NTOTALAMOUNT1-MSG
                MOVE COCK0002-CAPLIC
                                     TO COCV7811-NTOTALAMOUNT1-CAPLIC
             END-IF
           END-IF.

      *--- Descriçăo da Factura
           IF VIAL0002-SEM-ERROS
             IF COCV7810-GDESCINVOICE1 EQUAL SPACES
                MOVE VIAK0002-ERROS-FUNCAO  TO VIAL0002-IND-ERROS
                MOVE COCK0002-STATUS-ACTIVO
                                     TO COCV7811-GDESCINVOICE1-S
                MOVE COCK0001-CAMPO-OBRIGAT
                                     TO COCV7811-GDESCINVOICE1-MSG
                MOVE COCK0002-CAPLIC
                                     TO COCV7811-GDESCINVOICE1-CAPLIC
             END-IF
           END-IF.

      *--- Valores a positivo e negativo
           IF VIAL0002-SEM-ERROS
             IF  (COCV7810-NTOTALAMOUNT1 < ZEROS
             AND  COCV7810-NTAXAMOUNT1   > ZEROS)
             OR  (COCV7810-NTOTALAMOUNT1 > ZEROS
             AND  COCV7810-NTAXAMOUNT1   < ZEROS)
               MOVE VIAK0002-ERROS-FUNCAO  TO VIAL0002-IND-ERROS
               MOVE COCK0002-STATUS-ACTIVO TO COCV7811-NTAXAMOUNT1-S
               MOVE COCK0001-SINAL-ERRADO  TO COCV7811-NTAXAMOUNT1-MSG
               MOVE COCK0002-CAPLIC
                                        TO COCV7811-NTAXAMOUNT1-CAPLIC
             END-IF
           END-IF.

      *--- Valor Imposto versus Codigo Imposto
           IF VIAL0002-SEM-ERROS
             IF COCV7810-CIMPOSTO1       EQUAL SPACES
                MOVE VIAK0002-ERROS-FUNCAO  TO VIAL0002-IND-ERROS
                MOVE COCK0002-STATUS-ACTIVO TO COCV7811-CIMPOSTO1-S
                MOVE COCK0001-CAMPO-OBRIGAT TO COCV7811-CIMPOSTO1-MSG
                MOVE COCK0002-CAPLIC        TO COCV7811-CIMPOSTO1-CAPLIC
             END-IF
           END-IF.

           IF VIAL0002-SEM-ERROS
             INITIALIZE COCL5005-COMMAREA  REPLACING NUMERIC BY ZEROES
                                                ALPHANUMERIC BY SPACES

             MOVE ZEROS                      TO COCL5005-NTOTALAMOUNT
             MOVE SPACES                     TO COCL5005-CIMPOSTO
             MOVE ZEROS                      TO COCL5005-NTAXAMOUNT
             MOVE ZEROS                      TO COCL5005-NRETAMOUNT
             MOVE ZEROS                      TO COCL5005-NRETTAX
             MOVE ZEROS                      TO WS-NRETAMOUNT1
             MOVE ZEROS                      TO WS-NRETTAX1
             MOVE COCK0002-DATA-MIN          TO COCL5005-DDATAEMISS

             MOVE COCV7810-NTOTALAMOUNT1 TO COCL5005-NTOTALAMOUNT
             MOVE COCV7810-CIMPOSTO1     TO COCL5005-CIMPOSTO
             MOVE COCV7810-CMOEDA        TO COCL5005-CMOEDA
             MOVE COCD3605-PAIS          TO COCL5005-CPAIS
             MOVE COCK0002-EVEN-RECEITA  TO COCL5005-CTIP-EVEN
             MOVE COCD3605-CEMPRESA      TO COCL5005-CEMPRESA
             MOVE COCD3605-NIDPROJECTO   TO COCL5005-NIDPROJECTO
             MOVE ZEROES                 TO COCL5005-NIDINVOICE
             MOVE SPACES                 TO COCL5005-GFORNECED

             MOVE VIAL0001-DATA-PROCESSO-I TO COCL5005-DDATAEMISS

             IF COCV7810-DDATAEMISS1 NOT = SPACES AND
                COCV7810-DDATAEMISS1 NOT = COCK0002-DATA-MIN
               MOVE COCV7810-DDATAEMISS1 TO COCL5005-DDATAEMISS
             END-IF

             PERFORM 2100-VALIDA-IMPOSTO
                THRU 2100-VALIDA-IMPOSTO-EXIT

             IF NOT ETCL0002-SEM-ERROS
               MOVE ETCL0002-IND-ERROS     TO VIAL0002-IND-ERROS
               MOVE COCK0002-STATUS-ACTIVO TO COCV7811-CIMPOSTO1-S
               MOVE ETCL0002-NR-ERRO       TO COCV7811-CIMPOSTO1-MSG
               MOVE ETCL0002-CAPLIC-ERRO   TO COCV7811-CIMPOSTO1-CAPLIC
             ELSE
               MOVE COCL5005-NTAXAMOUNT    TO COCV7810-NTAXAMOUNT1
                                              COCV7811-NTAXAMOUNT1
               MOVE COCL5005-NRETAMOUNT    TO WS-NRETAMOUNT1
               MOVE COCL5005-NRETTAX       TO WS-NRETTAX1
             END-IF

           END-IF.

       2500-VALIDA-OC1-EXIT.
           EXIT.

      *--------------------------------------------------------------
      *--- 2500-VALIDACOES SEGUNDA OCORRENCIA
      *--------------------------------------------------------------
       2500-VALIDA-OC2.

           IF VIAL0001-DEBUG-SIM
              MOVE '2500-VALIDA-OC2' TO VIAL0015-CALLER-ID
              PERFORM VIAP0016-TRATA-DEBUG
                 THRU VIAP0016-TRATA-DEBUG-EXIT
           END-IF.

      *--- Data Prevista de Emissao
           IF VIAL0002-SEM-ERROS
             IF COCV7810-DDATAEMISS2 EQUAL SPACES
             OR COCV7810-DDATAEMISS2 EQUAL COCK0002-DATA-MIN
                MOVE VIAK0002-ERROS-FUNCAO  TO VIAL0002-IND-ERROS
                MOVE COCK0002-STATUS-ACTIVO TO COCV7811-DDATAEMISS2-S
                MOVE COCK0001-CAMPO-OBRIGAT TO COCV7811-DDATAEMISS2-MSG
                MOVE COCK0002-CAPLIC     TO COCV7811-DDATAEMISS2-CAPLIC
             END-IF
           END-IF.

      *--- Data de Vencimento
           IF VIAL0002-SEM-ERROS
             IF COCV7810-DDATEDUE2   EQUAL SPACES
             OR COCV7810-DDATEDUE2   EQUAL COCK0002-DATA-MIN
                MOVE VIAK0002-ERROS-FUNCAO  TO VIAL0002-IND-ERROS
                MOVE COCK0002-STATUS-ACTIVO TO COCV7811-DDATEDUE2-S
                MOVE COCK0001-CAMPO-OBRIGAT TO COCV7811-DDATEDUE2-MSG
                MOVE COCK0002-CAPLIC     TO COCV7811-DDATEDUE2-CAPLIC
             END-IF
           END-IF.

      *--- Data de Vencimento versus Data Prevista de Emissao
           IF VIAL0002-SEM-ERROS
             IF  COCV7810-DDATEDUE2 NOT EQUAL SPACES
             AND COCV7810-DDATEDUE2 NOT EQUAL COCK0002-DATA-MIN
             AND COCV7810-DDATEDUE2 < COCV7810-DDATAEMISS2
                MOVE VIAK0002-ERROS-FUNCAO  TO VIAL0002-IND-ERROS
                MOVE COCK0002-STATUS-ACTIVO TO COCV7811-DDATEDUE2-S
                MOVE COCK0001-DTVEN-INV     TO COCV7811-DDATEDUE2-MSG
                MOVE COCK0002-CAPLIC     TO COCV7811-DDATEDUE2-CAPLIC
             END-IF

      *--- Prazo Vencimento
           IF VIAL0002-SEM-ERROS
             IF COCV7810-CPRAZO2 EQUAL SPACES
                MOVE VIAK0002-ERROS-FUNCAO  TO VIAL0002-IND-ERROS
                MOVE COCK0002-STATUS-ACTIVO TO COCV7811-CPRAZO2-S
                MOVE COCK0001-CAMPO-OBRIGAT TO COCV7811-CPRAZO2-MSG
                MOVE COCK0002-CAPLIC     TO COCV7811-CPRAZO2-CAPLIC
             END-IF
           END-IF.

      *--- Tipo de Factura
           IF VIAL0002-SEM-ERROS
             IF COCV7810-CTIPFAC2 EQUAL SPACES
                MOVE VIAK0002-ERROS-FUNCAO  TO VIAL0002-IND-ERROS
                MOVE COCK0002-STATUS-ACTIVO TO COCV7811-CTIPFAC2-S
                MOVE COCK0001-CAMPO-OBRIGAT TO COCV7811-CTIPFAC2-MSG
                MOVE COCK0002-CAPLIC     TO COCV7811-CTIPFAC2-CAPLIC
             END-IF
           END-IF.

      *--- Valor Liquido
           IF VIAL0002-SEM-ERROS
             IF COCV7810-NTOTALAMOUNT2 EQUAL ZEROS
                MOVE VIAK0002-ERROS-FUNCAO  TO VIAL0002-IND-ERROS
                MOVE COCK0002-STATUS-ACTIVO
                                     TO COCV7811-NTOTALAMOUNT2-S
                MOVE COCK0001-CAMPO-OBRIGAT
                                     TO COCV7811-NTOTALAMOUNT2-MSG
                MOVE COCK0002-CAPLIC
                                     TO COCV7811-NTOTALAMOUNT2-CAPLIC
             END-IF
           END-IF.

      *--- Descriçăo da Factura
           IF VIAL0002-SEM-ERROS
             IF COCV7810-GDESCINVOICE2 EQUAL SPACES
                MOVE VIAK0002-ERROS-FUNCAO  TO VIAL0002-IND-ERROS
                MOVE COCK0002-STATUS-ACTIVO
                                     TO COCV7811-GDESCINVOICE2-S
                MOVE COCK0001-CAMPO-OBRIGAT
                                     TO COCV7811-GDESCINVOICE2-MSG
                MOVE COCK0002-CAPLIC
                                     TO COCV7811-GDESCINVOICE2-CAPLIC
             END-IF
           END-IF.

      *--- Valores a positivo e negativo
           IF VIAL0002-SEM-ERROS
             IF  (COCV7810-NTOTALAMOUNT2 < ZEROS
             AND  COCV7810-NTAXAMOUNT2   > ZEROS)
             OR  (COCV7810-NTOTALAMOUNT2 > ZEROS
             AND  COCV7810-NTAXAMOUNT2   < ZEROS)
               MOVE VIAK0002-ERROS-FUNCAO  TO VIAL0002-IND-ERROS
               MOVE COCK0002-STATUS-ACTIVO TO COCV7811-NTAXAMOUNT2-S
               MOVE COCK0001-SINAL-ERRADO  TO COCV7811-NTAXAMOUNT2-MSG
               MOVE COCK0002-CAPLIC
                                        TO COCV7811-NTAXAMOUNT2-CAPLIC
             END-IF
           END-IF.

      *--- Valor Imposto versus Codigo Imposto
           IF VIAL0002-SEM-ERROS
             IF COCV7810-CIMPOSTO2       EQUAL SPACES
                MOVE VIAK0002-ERROS-FUNCAO  TO VIAL0002-IND-ERROS
                MOVE COCK0002-STATUS-ACTIVO TO COCV7811-CIMPOSTO2-S
                MOVE COCK0001-CAMPO-OBRIGAT TO COCV7811-CIMPOSTO2-MSG
                MOVE COCK0002-CAPLIC        TO COCV7811-CIMPOSTO2-CAPLIC
             END-IF
           END-IF.

           IF VIAL0002-SEM-ERROS
             INITIALIZE COCL5005-COMMAREA  REPLACING NUMERIC BY ZEROES
                                                ALPHANUMERIC BY SPACES

             MOVE ZEROS                      TO COCL5005-NTOTALAMOUNT
             MOVE SPACES                     TO COCL5005-CIMPOSTO
             MOVE ZEROS                      TO COCL5005-NTAXAMOUNT
             MOVE ZEROS                      TO COCL5005-NRETAMOUNT
             MOVE ZEROS                      TO COCL5005-NRETTAX
             MOVE ZEROS                      TO WS-NRETAMOUNT2
             MOVE ZEROS                      TO WS-NRETTAX2
             MOVE COCK0002-DATA-MIN          TO COCL5005-DDATAEMISS

             MOVE COCV7810-NTOTALAMOUNT2 TO COCL5005-NTOTALAMOUNT
             MOVE COCV7810-CIMPOSTO2     TO COCL5005-CIMPOSTO
             MOVE COCV7810-CMOEDA        TO COCL5005-CMOEDA
             MOVE COCD3605-PAIS          TO COCL5005-CPAIS
             MOVE COCK0002-EVEN-RECEITA  TO COCL5005-CTIP-EVEN
             MOVE COCD3605-CEMPRESA      TO COCL5005-CEMPRESA
             MOVE COCD3605-NIDPROJECTO   TO COCL5005-NIDPROJECTO
             MOVE ZEROES                 TO COCL5005-NIDINVOICE
             MOVE SPACES                 TO COCL5005-GFORNECED

             MOVE VIAL0001-DATA-PROCESSO-I TO COCL5005-DDATAEMISS

             IF COCV7810-DDATAEMISS2 NOT = SPACES AND
                COCV7810-DDATAEMISS2 NOT = COCK0002-DATA-MIN
               MOVE COCV7810-DDATAEMISS2 TO COCL5005-DDATAEMISS
             END-IF

             PERFORM 2100-VALIDA-IMPOSTO
                THRU 2100-VALIDA-IMPOSTO-EXIT

             IF NOT ETCL0002-SEM-ERROS
               MOVE ETCL0002-IND-ERROS     TO VIAL0002-IND-ERROS
               MOVE COCK0002-STATUS-ACTIVO TO COCV7811-CIMPOSTO2-S
               MOVE ETCL0002-NR-ERRO       TO COCV7811-CIMPOSTO2-MSG
               MOVE ETCL0002-CAPLIC-ERRO   TO COCV7811-CIMPOSTO2-CAPLIC
             ELSE
               MOVE COCL5005-NTAXAMOUNT    TO COCV7810-NTAXAMOUNT2
                                              COCV7811-NTAXAMOUNT2
               MOVE COCL5005-NRETAMOUNT    TO WS-NRETAMOUNT2
               MOVE COCL5005-NRETTAX       TO WS-NRETTAX2
             END-IF

           END-IF.

       2500-VALIDA-OC2-EXIT.
           EXIT.

      *--------------------------------------------------------------
      *--- 2500-VALIDACOES TERCEIRA OCORRENCIA
      *--------------------------------------------------------------
       2500-VALIDA-OC3.

           IF VIAL0001-DEBUG-SIM
              MOVE '2500-VALIDA-OC3' TO VIAL0015-CALLER-ID
              PERFORM VIAP0016-TRATA-DEBUG
                 THRU VIAP0016-TRATA-DEBUG-EXIT
           END-IF.

      *--- Data Prevista de Emissao
           IF VIAL0002-SEM-ERROS
             IF COCV7810-DDATAEMISS3 EQUAL SPACES
             OR COCV7810-DDATAEMISS3 EQUAL COCK0002-DATA-MIN
                MOVE VIAK0002-ERROS-FUNCAO  TO VIAL0002-IND-ERROS
                MOVE COCK0002-STATUS-ACTIVO TO COCV7811-DDATAEMISS3-S
                MOVE COCK0001-CAMPO-OBRIGAT TO COCV7811-DDATAEMISS3-MSG
                MOVE COCK0002-CAPLIC     TO COCV7811-DDATAEMISS3-CAPLIC
             END-IF
           END-IF.

      *--- Data de Vencimento
           IF VIAL0002-SEM-ERROS
             IF COCV7810-DDATEDUE3   EQUAL SPACES
             OR COCV7810-DDATEDUE3   EQUAL COCK0002-DATA-MIN
                MOVE VIAK0002-ERROS-FUNCAO  TO VIAL0002-IND-ERROS
                MOVE COCK0002-STATUS-ACTIVO TO COCV7811-DDATEDUE3-S
                MOVE COCK0001-CAMPO-OBRIGAT TO COCV7811-DDATEDUE3-MSG
                MOVE COCK0002-CAPLIC     TO COCV7811-DDATEDUE3-CAPLIC
             END-IF
           END-IF.

      *--- Data de Vencimento versus Data Prevista de Emissao
           IF VIAL0002-SEM-ERROS
             IF  COCV7810-DDATEDUE3 NOT EQUAL SPACES
             AND COCV7810-DDATEDUE3 NOT EQUAL COCK0002-DATA-MIN
             AND COCV7810-DDATEDUE3 < COCV7810-DDATAEMISS3
                MOVE VIAK0002-ERROS-FUNCAO  TO VIAL0002-IND-ERROS
                MOVE COCK0002-STATUS-ACTIVO TO COCV7811-DDATEDUE3-S
                MOVE COCK0001-DTVEN-INV     TO COCV7811-DDATEDUE3-MSG
                MOVE COCK0002-CAPLIC     TO COCV7811-DDATEDUE3-CAPLIC
             END-IF

      *--- Prazo Vencimento
           IF VIAL0002-SEM-ERROS
             IF COCV7810-CPRAZO3 EQUAL SPACES
                MOVE VIAK0002-ERROS-FUNCAO  TO VIAL0002-IND-ERROS
                MOVE COCK0002-STATUS-ACTIVO TO COCV7811-CPRAZO3-S
                MOVE COCK0001-CAMPO-OBRIGAT TO COCV7811-CPRAZO3-MSG
                MOVE COCK0002-CAPLIC     TO COCV7811-CPRAZO3-CAPLIC
             END-IF
           END-IF.

      *--- Tipo de Factura
           IF VIAL0002-SEM-ERROS
             IF COCV7810-CTIPFAC3 EQUAL SPACES
                MOVE VIAK0002-ERROS-FUNCAO  TO VIAL0002-IND-ERROS
                MOVE COCK0002-STATUS-ACTIVO TO COCV7811-CTIPFAC3-S
                MOVE COCK0001-CAMPO-OBRIGAT TO COCV7811-CTIPFAC3-MSG
                MOVE COCK0002-CAPLIC     TO COCV7811-CTIPFAC3-CAPLIC
             END-IF
           END-IF.

      *--- Valor Liquido
           IF VIAL0002-SEM-ERROS
             IF COCV7810-NTOTALAMOUNT3 EQUAL ZEROS
                MOVE VIAK0002-ERROS-FUNCAO  TO VIAL0002-IND-ERROS
                MOVE COCK0002-STATUS-ACTIVO
                                     TO COCV7811-NTOTALAMOUNT3-S
                MOVE COCK0001-CAMPO-OBRIGAT
                                     TO COCV7811-NTOTALAMOUNT3-MSG
                MOVE COCK0002-CAPLIC
                                     TO COCV7811-NTOTALAMOUNT3-CAPLIC
             END-IF
           END-IF.

      *--- Descriçăo da Factura
           IF VIAL0002-SEM-ERROS
             IF COCV7810-GDESCINVOICE3 EQUAL SPACES
                MOVE VIAK0002-ERROS-FUNCAO  TO VIAL0002-IND-ERROS
                MOVE COCK0002-STATUS-ACTIVO
                                     TO COCV7811-GDESCINVOICE3-S
                MOVE COCK0001-CAMPO-OBRIGAT
                                     TO COCV7811-GDESCINVOICE3-MSG
                MOVE COCK0002-CAPLIC
                                     TO COCV7811-GDESCINVOICE3-CAPLIC
             END-IF
           END-IF.

      *--- Valores a positivo e negativo
           IF VIAL0002-SEM-ERROS
             IF  (COCV7810-NTOTALAMOUNT3 < ZEROS
             AND  COCV7810-NTAXAMOUNT3   > ZEROS)
             OR  (COCV7810-NTOTALAMOUNT3 > ZEROS
             AND  COCV7810-NTAXAMOUNT3   < ZEROS)
               MOVE VIAK0002-ERROS-FUNCAO  TO VIAL0002-IND-ERROS
               MOVE COCK0002-STATUS-ACTIVO TO COCV7811-NTAXAMOUNT3-S
               MOVE COCK0001-SINAL-ERRADO  TO COCV7811-NTAXAMOUNT3-MSG
               MOVE COCK0002-CAPLIC
                                        TO COCV7811-NTAXAMOUNT3-CAPLIC
             END-IF
           END-IF.

      *--- Valor Imposto versus Codigo Imposto
           IF VIAL0002-SEM-ERROS
             IF COCV7810-CIMPOSTO3       EQUAL SPACES
                MOVE VIAK0002-ERROS-FUNCAO  TO VIAL0002-IND-ERROS
                MOVE COCK0002-STATUS-ACTIVO TO COCV7811-CIMPOSTO3-S
                MOVE COCK0001-CAMPO-OBRIGAT TO COCV7811-CIMPOSTO3-MSG
                MOVE COCK0002-CAPLIC        TO COCV7811-CIMPOSTO3-CAPLIC
             END-IF
           END-IF.

           IF VIAL0002-SEM-ERROS
             INITIALIZE COCL5005-COMMAREA  REPLACING NUMERIC BY ZEROES
                                                ALPHANUMERIC BY SPACES

             MOVE ZEROS                      TO COCL5005-NTOTALAMOUNT
             MOVE SPACES                     TO COCL5005-CIMPOSTO
             MOVE ZEROS                      TO COCL5005-NTAXAMOUNT
             MOVE ZEROS                      TO COCL5005-NRETAMOUNT
             MOVE ZEROS                      TO COCL5005-NRETTAX
             MOVE ZEROS                      TO WS-NRETAMOUNT3
             MOVE ZEROS                      TO WS-NRETTAX3
             MOVE COCK0002-DATA-MIN          TO COCL5005-DDATAEMISS

             MOVE COCV7810-NTOTALAMOUNT3 TO COCL5005-NTOTALAMOUNT
             MOVE COCV7810-CIMPOSTO3     TO COCL5005-CIMPOSTO
             MOVE COCV7810-CMOEDA        TO COCL5005-CMOEDA
             MOVE COCD3605-PAIS          TO COCL5005-CPAIS
             MOVE COCK0002-EVEN-RECEITA  TO COCL5005-CTIP-EVEN
             MOVE COCD3605-CEMPRESA      TO COCL5005-CEMPRESA
             MOVE COCD3605-NIDPROJECTO   TO COCL5005-NIDPROJECTO
             MOVE ZEROES                 TO COCL5005-NIDINVOICE
             MOVE SPACES                 TO COCL5005-GFORNECED

             MOVE VIAL0001-DATA-PROCESSO-I TO COCL5005-DDATAEMISS

             IF COCV7810-DDATAEMISS3 NOT = SPACES AND
                COCV7810-DDATAEMISS3 NOT = COCK0002-DATA-MIN
               MOVE COCV7810-DDATAEMISS3 TO COCL5005-DDATAEMISS
             END-IF

             PERFORM 2100-VALIDA-IMPOSTO
                THRU 2100-VALIDA-IMPOSTO-EXIT

             IF NOT ETCL0002-SEM-ERROS
               MOVE ETCL0002-IND-ERROS     TO VIAL0002-IND-ERROS
               MOVE COCK0002-STATUS-ACTIVO TO COCV7811-CIMPOSTO3-S
               MOVE ETCL0002-NR-ERRO       TO COCV7811-CIMPOSTO3-MSG
               MOVE ETCL0002-CAPLIC-ERRO   TO COCV7811-CIMPOSTO3-CAPLIC
             ELSE
               MOVE COCL5005-NTAXAMOUNT    TO COCV7810-NTAXAMOUNT3
                                              COCV7811-NTAXAMOUNT3
               MOVE COCL5005-NRETAMOUNT    TO WS-NRETAMOUNT3
               MOVE COCL5005-NRETTAX       TO WS-NRETTAX3
             END-IF

           END-IF.

       2500-VALIDA-OC3-EXIT.
           EXIT.

      *--------------------------------------------------------------
      *--- 2500-VALIDACOES QUARTA OCORRENCIA
      *--------------------------------------------------------------
       2500-VALIDA-OC4.

           IF VIAL0001-DEBUG-SIM
              MOVE '2500-VALIDA-OC4' TO VIAL0015-CALLER-ID
              PERFORM VIAP0016-TRATA-DEBUG
                 THRU VIAP0016-TRATA-DEBUG-EXIT
           END-IF.

      *--- Data de Prevista de Emissao
           IF VIAL0002-SEM-ERROS
             IF COCV7810-DDATAEMISS4 EQUAL SPACES
             OR COCV7810-DDATAEMISS4 EQUAL COCK0002-DATA-MIN
                MOVE VIAK0002-ERROS-FUNCAO  TO VIAL0002-IND-ERROS
                MOVE COCK0002-STATUS-ACTIVO TO COCV7811-DDATAEMISS4-S
                MOVE COCK0001-CAMPO-OBRIGAT TO COCV7811-DDATAEMISS4-MSG
                MOVE COCK0002-CAPLIC     TO COCV7811-DDATAEMISS4-CAPLIC
             END-IF
           END-IF.

      *--- Data de Vencimento
           IF VIAL0002-SEM-ERROS
             IF COCV7810-DDATEDUE4   EQUAL SPACES
             OR COCV7810-DDATEDUE4   EQUAL COCK0002-DATA-MIN
                MOVE VIAK0002-ERROS-FUNCAO  TO VIAL0002-IND-ERROS
                MOVE COCK0002-STATUS-ACTIVO TO COCV7811-DDATEDUE4-S
                MOVE COCK0001-CAMPO-OBRIGAT TO COCV7811-DDATEDUE4-MSG
                MOVE COCK0002-CAPLIC     TO COCV7811-DDATEDUE4-CAPLIC
             END-IF
           END-IF.

      *--- Data de Vencimento versus Data Prevista de Emissao
           IF VIAL0002-SEM-ERROS
             IF  COCV7810-DDATEDUE4 NOT EQUAL SPACES
             AND COCV7810-DDATEDUE4 NOT EQUAL COCK0002-DATA-MIN
             AND COCV7810-DDATEDUE4 < COCV7810-DDATAEMISS4
                MOVE VIAK0002-ERROS-FUNCAO  TO VIAL0002-IND-ERROS
                MOVE COCK0002-STATUS-ACTIVO TO COCV7811-DDATEDUE4-S
                MOVE COCK0001-DTVEN-INV     TO COCV7811-DDATEDUE4-MSG
                MOVE COCK0002-CAPLIC     TO COCV7811-DDATEDUE4-CAPLIC
             END-IF

      *--- Prazo Vencimento
           IF VIAL0002-SEM-ERROS
             IF COCV7810-CPRAZO4 EQUAL SPACES
                MOVE VIAK0002-ERROS-FUNCAO  TO VIAL0002-IND-ERROS
                MOVE COCK0002-STATUS-ACTIVO TO COCV7811-CPRAZO4-S
                MOVE COCK0001-CAMPO-OBRIGAT TO COCV7811-CPRAZO4-MSG
                MOVE COCK0002-CAPLIC     TO COCV7811-CPRAZO4-CAPLIC
             END-IF
           END-IF.

      *--- Tipo de Factura
           IF VIAL0002-SEM-ERROS
             IF COCV7810-CTIPFAC4 EQUAL SPACES
                MOVE VIAK0002-ERROS-FUNCAO  TO VIAL0002-IND-ERROS
                MOVE COCK0002-STATUS-ACTIVO TO COCV7811-CTIPFAC4-S
                MOVE COCK0001-CAMPO-OBRIGAT TO COCV7811-CTIPFAC4-MSG
                MOVE COCK0002-CAPLIC     TO COCV7811-CTIPFAC4-CAPLIC
             END-IF
           END-IF.

      *--- Valor Liquido
           IF VIAL0002-SEM-ERROS
             IF COCV7810-NTOTALAMOUNT4 EQUAL ZEROS
                MOVE VIAK0002-ERROS-FUNCAO  TO VIAL0002-IND-ERROS
                MOVE COCK0002-STATUS-ACTIVO
                                     TO COCV7811-NTOTALAMOUNT4-S
                MOVE COCK0001-CAMPO-OBRIGAT
                                     TO COCV7811-NTOTALAMOUNT4-MSG
                MOVE COCK0002-CAPLIC
                                     TO COCV7811-NTOTALAMOUNT4-CAPLIC
             END-IF
           END-IF.

      *--- Descriçăo da Factura
           IF VIAL0002-SEM-ERROS
             IF COCV7810-GDESCINVOICE4 EQUAL SPACES
                MOVE VIAK0002-ERROS-FUNCAO  TO VIAL0002-IND-ERROS
                MOVE COCK0002-STATUS-ACTIVO
                                     TO COCV7811-GDESCINVOICE4-S
                MOVE COCK0001-CAMPO-OBRIGAT
                                     TO COCV7811-GDESCINVOICE4-MSG
                MOVE COCK0002-CAPLIC
                                     TO COCV7811-GDESCINVOICE4-CAPLIC
             END-IF
           END-IF.

      *--- Valores a positivo e negativo
           IF VIAL0002-SEM-ERROS
             IF  (COCV7810-NTOTALAMOUNT4 < ZEROS
             AND  COCV7810-NTAXAMOUNT4   > ZEROS)
             OR  (COCV7810-NTOTALAMOUNT4 > ZEROS
             AND  COCV7810-NTAXAMOUNT4   < ZEROS)
               MOVE VIAK0002-ERROS-FUNCAO  TO VIAL0002-IND-ERROS
               MOVE COCK0002-STATUS-ACTIVO TO COCV7811-NTAXAMOUNT4-S
               MOVE COCK0001-SINAL-ERRADO  TO COCV7811-NTAXAMOUNT4-MSG
               MOVE COCK0002-CAPLIC
                                        TO COCV7811-NTAXAMOUNT4-CAPLIC
             END-IF
           END-IF.

      *--- Valor Imposto versus Codigo Imposto
           IF VIAL0002-SEM-ERROS
             IF COCV7810-CIMPOSTO4       EQUAL SPACES
                MOVE VIAK0002-ERROS-FUNCAO  TO VIAL0002-IND-ERROS
                MOVE COCK0002-STATUS-ACTIVO TO COCV7811-CIMPOSTO4-S
                MOVE COCK0001-CAMPO-OBRIGAT TO COCV7811-CIMPOSTO4-MSG
                MOVE COCK0002-CAPLIC        TO COCV7811-CIMPOSTO4-CAPLIC
             END-IF
           END-IF.

           IF VIAL0002-SEM-ERROS
             INITIALIZE COCL5005-COMMAREA  REPLACING NUMERIC BY ZEROES
                                                ALPHANUMERIC BY SPACES

             MOVE ZEROS                      TO COCL5005-NTOTALAMOUNT
             MOVE SPACES                     TO COCL5005-CIMPOSTO
             MOVE ZEROS                      TO COCL5005-NTAXAMOUNT
             MOVE ZEROS                      TO COCL5005-NRETAMOUNT
             MOVE ZEROS                      TO COCL5005-NRETTAX
             MOVE ZEROS                      TO WS-NRETAMOUNT4
             MOVE ZEROS                      TO WS-NRETTAX4
             MOVE COCK0002-DATA-MIN          TO COCL5005-DDATAEMISS

             MOVE COCV7810-NTOTALAMOUNT4 TO COCL5005-NTOTALAMOUNT
             MOVE COCV7810-CIMPOSTO4     TO COCL5005-CIMPOSTO
             MOVE COCV7810-CMOEDA        TO COCL5005-CMOEDA
             MOVE COCD3605-PAIS          TO COCL5005-CPAIS
             MOVE COCK0002-EVEN-RECEITA  TO COCL5005-CTIP-EVEN
             MOVE COCD3605-CEMPRESA      TO COCL5005-CEMPRESA
             MOVE COCD3605-NIDPROJECTO   TO COCL5005-NIDPROJECTO
             MOVE ZEROES                 TO COCL5005-NIDINVOICE
             MOVE SPACES                 TO COCL5005-GFORNECED

             MOVE VIAL0001-DATA-PROCESSO-I TO COCL5005-DDATAEMISS

             IF COCV7810-DDATAEMISS4 NOT = SPACES AND
                COCV7810-DDATAEMISS4 NOT = COCK0002-DATA-MIN
               MOVE COCV7810-DDATAEMISS4 TO COCL5005-DDATAEMISS
             END-IF

             PERFORM 2100-VALIDA-IMPOSTO
                THRU 2100-VALIDA-IMPOSTO-EXIT

             IF NOT ETCL0002-SEM-ERROS
               MOVE ETCL0002-IND-ERROS     TO VIAL0002-IND-ERROS
               MOVE COCK0002-STATUS-ACTIVO TO COCV7811-CIMPOSTO4-S
               MOVE ETCL0002-NR-ERRO       TO COCV7811-CIMPOSTO4-MSG
               MOVE ETCL0002-CAPLIC-ERRO   TO COCV7811-CIMPOSTO4-CAPLIC
